{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/texts/tipitaka/sutta-pitaka/samyutta-nikaya/SN1/acchara-sutta/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>“It’s resounding with a group of nymphs, <br>\nbut haunted by a gang of goblins! <br>\nThis grove is called ‘Delusion’. <br>\nHow am I supposed to live like this?” <br>\n<br>\n“That path is called ‘the straight way’, <br>\nand it’s headed for the place called ‘fearless’. <br>\nThe chariot is called ‘unswerving’, <br>\nfitted with wheels of skillful thoughts. <br>\n<br>\nConscience is its bench-back, <br>\nmindfulness its upholstery. <br>\nI say the teaching is the driver, <br>\nwith right view running out in front. <br>\n<br>\nAny woman or man <br>\nwho has such a vehicle, <br>\nby means of this vehicle <br>\nhas drawn near to extinguishment.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n<p><a href=\"/texts/tipitaka/sutta-pitaka/samyutta-nikaya/SN1/vanaropa-sutta/\">SN.1.47. Vanaropa Sutta (“Planters”)</a></p>\n</div>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“It’s resounding with a group of nymphs, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nbut haunted by a gang of goblins! "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nThis grove is called ‘Delusion’. "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nHow am I supposed to live like this?” "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n“That path is called ‘the straight way’, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nan